      "content": "hey so i work in customer service and i have this really unhappy customer. they bought a super expensive espresso machine like two weeks ago and it still hasn't arrived because of some mess up with the shipping company. i need to write an email to them to apologize and explain what happened without sounding like we just dont care. can u help me draft something professional?",
